            "title": "華勤技術首掛高收逾13% 每手賬賺1030元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">華勤技術(03296)今日登場，全日穩企於招股價77.7元之上，收報88元，較招股價高13.26%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"華勤技術官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/603296-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"華勤技術官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/603296-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">華勤技術官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">以該股1手100股計，認購並獲配每手賬面賺1030元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該股今早以87.55元開市，全日最低報85元時仍高於招股價9.4%；高位報90.95元，更較招股價高17.05%，全日成交21.49億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">華勤技術A股(603296.SH)今日則跟隨內地股市回吐，收報103.86元人民幣，跌1.16%。</p>\n</div>",
